            </div>
            <div class="problems__grid">
                <article class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Confusing interfaces</h3>
                    <p>Your users struggle to navigate your product, leading to frustration and decreased engagement.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Low conversion rates</h3>
                    <p>Poor UX design creates friction in your user journey, resulting in high bounce rates and abandoned purchases.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Outdated design</h3>
                    <p>Your product looks dated compared to competitors, undermining user trust and perceived value.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
